### AI Code Documentation Generator API Tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

### 1. Authentication Tests

### Register User
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/me
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Google OAuth Login
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/google

### Logout
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/logout

### 2. Project Management Tests

### Upload Project (Protected)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/projects/upload
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Test Project
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

A test project for API testing
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="test.js"
Content-Type: application/javascript

function hello() {
  console.log("Hello World!");
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Get User Projects (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/projects
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Get Project by ID (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Get Project Stats (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE/stats
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Delete Project (Protected)
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

