### 5. History & Analytics Tests

### Get User History (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/history
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Get User History with Type Filter (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/history?type=projects&page=1&limit=5
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Get User Statistics (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/history/stats
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Search History (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/history/search?query=test&type=projects
Cookie: token=your_jwt_token_here

### Notes:
# 1. Replace 'your_jwt_token_here' with actual JWT token from login response
# 2. Replace 'PROJECT_ID_HERE', 'DOC_ID_HERE', 'UML_ID_HERE' with actual IDs
# 3. Make sure to set up environment variables before testing
# 4. For file upload, you can use tools like Postman or Insomnia for better multipart support